The copyright material is identified by  

Images of Jasmine Hemsley in lingerie swimwear or nightwear on a grey or  

white background. May have also been cropped into headshot or body parts  

and may have been modified into wallpapers and colours changed. These  
images were used for the sole purpose on Debenhams website. They no longer
 
exist on this website as they were used to sell the garments on this  
e-commerce website exclusively.
